data.title: NYC in a day: Private Walking Tour with the Statue of Liberty
data.meta_description: Immerse yourself in Lower Manhattan, travel to the Liberty & Ellis Islands to see the Statue of Liberty, visit Ground Zero and explore the 9/11 Memorial Museum on this NYC in a day private tour.
data.text:
Explore the best of New York in a day on a private tour from lower Manhattan & Ground Zero to Times Square including tickets for the Top of the Rock (the Rockefeller Center observation deck)

Experience the magic of New York City dressed up in Christmas lights & holiday cheer and discover the iconic landmarks, such as the Rockefeller Center at its most enchanting!
